column2: "Yo, <%me>. Have you had a chance to tour the ship's new layout?"
"I directed the renovations. If you wanna freshen things up, you gotta start with a new look, y'know?"
"What should we improve next, hm? We could start with hmm... ooh, maybe..."
"Ulc's been like this ever since Xiao put her in Logistics."
"She's pushing the limits of her job description. I can barely keep up with her assignments."
"Heh, you can say that again. But as long as she's happy, I can handle it."
"Is that how it looks? ...well, as long as she's happy, I can handle it."
"Seeing her smile... makes me happy too."
